comments.body:
The files with the mapped values are checked in config/locations/holding_locations.json and delivery_locations.json. 
If we want to recreate them we would need to run the rake task `bundle exec rspec locations:delivery_holding_locations`. 
To populate the tables locally or on bibdata we would need to run from the rails console `LocationDataService.delete_existing_and_repopulate`
This ticket is not accurate.
